stanzione robert j  the wall street transcript robert j stanzione robert j stanzione is president and chief executive officer of arris group inc arris is a new company formed by the merger of antec and arris interactive llc in august  arris is a global communications technology leader in the development of advanced cable telephony solutions and the delivery of converged services across the broadband local access network mr stanzione joined antec in  as president chief operating officer and a director and was appointed to the ceo role on january   prior to joining antec he was the president and ceo of arris interactive a nortel networksantec joint venture as arris’ first president mr stanzione grew the venture from a startup company to the world market leader in cable telephony products from  to  mr stanzione held a wide range of senior management positions with att network systems now lucent his last position with att before joining arris was as vice president consumer broadband networks a business unit focused on bringing ‘broadband’ to homes over phone and cable networks he holds a bs degree in mechanical engineering from clemson university an me degree in industrial engineering from north carolina state university and has completed executive development programs at the university of richmond babson college and the international institute for management development in switzerland he serves as a director of coaxmedia and evolve products inc he also serves as chairman of the georgia cystic fibrosis major gifts campaign related interviewsrobert stanzione  arris group inc arrsseptember  robert stanzione  arris group inc arrsmay  robert stanzione  arris group inc arrsjanuary  robert stanzione  arris group inc arrsseptember  robert stanzione  arris group inc arrsapril  robert stanzione  antec corporation antcjune  robert stanzione  antec corporation antcapril   cartlatest newsjames abate of centre asset management sees consumer demand driving new stock highsmalcolm e po